condition.narrative: Finance Agreement :Loan Agreement, Schedule 2, Section II, Part A, para 1 | Description :Borrower and Yunnan will monitor andevaluate project progress, prepare semi-annual reports and submit reports to the Bank March/Sept, starting March 15, 2012 |Frequency :Yearly

Finance Agreement :Loan Agreement, Schedule 2, Section II, Part B, para 2 | Description :Borrower and Yunnan to prepare & furnishto the Bank by March 15/Sept 15 annually interim unaudited financial reports | Frequency :Yearly

Finance Agreement :Loan Agreement, Schedule 2, Section II, Part B, para 3 | Description :Borrower and Yunnan to have financialstatements audited and submit audit to Bank not later than 6 months after close of period audited | Frequency :Yearly

Finance Agreement :Project Agreement, Annex A to Schedule, para 8 | Description :KRTC to have financial statements for each FYaudited; furnish audit to Bank within 6 months of close of period audited | Frequency :Yearly

Finance Agreement :Project Agreement, Schedule, Section I, Part A, para 3 | Description :Yunnan to prepare annual work plan andfurnish to Bank by Feb 15 annually starting Feb 15, 2011 | Frequency :Yearly

Finance Agreement :Project Agreement, Schedule, Section I, Part C, para 1 | Description :Prior to commencement of works, implementRAP. If design modification gives rise to Displaced Persons, provide RAP to Bank for review | Frequency :Yearly
